00:45:30.760 --> 00:45:33.200
I won’t stop, what will you do?

00:45:33.200 --> 00:45:35.040
Let go!

00:45:35.040 --> 00:45:36.480
Saint!

00:45:37.200 --> 00:45:39.200
What are you doing?

