Don’t!

00:46:06.040 --> 00:46:07.080
Stay still!

00:46:07.080 --> 00:46:09.280
It hurts, Saint, let me go!

00:46:09.280 --> 00:46:10.400
Why are you so strong?

00:46:10.400 --> 00:46:11.920
Saint, let me go!

00:46:11.920 --> 00:46:13.080
Stay still!

00:46:14.880 --> 00:46:16.880
What are you doing?

