Tell me honestly

00:47:53.560 --> 00:47:55.920
do you really think I’d bully your song?

00:47:55.920 --> 00:47:57.920
What do you take me for?

00:47:59.000 --> 00:48:00.520
Looking at me now

00:48:00.520 --> 00:48:02.920
that’s exactly the kind of person you are.

00:48:30.080 --> 00:48:34.840
I’m sorry, I know it’s not enough

00:48:37.560 --> 00:48:39.560
but still, I’m sorry.

00:48:53.360 --> 00:48:55.080
(P’Sea)

00:48:57.680 --> 00:49:02.920
Untie me first, P’Sea is calling, hurry!

00:49:02.920 --> 00:49:06.480
Nope, you’ll just punch me.

