Don’t you think Kit is too harsh on Sin?

00:50:23.000 --> 00:50:24.600
Such a red flag.

00:50:24.600 --> 00:50:27.880
True, but we have to understand

00:50:27.880 --> 00:50:30.640
that the social context backthen was different.

00:50:30.640 --> 00:50:33.000
He was under heavy pressure from society.

00:50:33.000 --> 00:50:35.240
So sexual aggression was stronger

00:50:35.240 --> 00:50:36.280
than in today’s world.

00:50:36.280 --> 00:50:38.400
That’s what our film is trying to show.

00:50:38.400 --> 00:50:39.840
Any other questions?

00:50:39.840 --> 00:50:42.920
If I play with my eyes closed like this

00:50:42.920 --> 00:50:44.240
how do I act?

00:50:44.240 --> 00:50:46.280
Just act like you can’t see your partner.

00:50:46.280 --> 00:50:48.440
The real Sin couldn’t see, he was in pain.

00:50:48.440 --> 00:50:50.840
This NC scene is crucial.

00:50:50.840 --> 00:50:54.720
We need an actor with fiery chemistry with you.

00:50:54.720 --> 00:50:56.400
Even if you can’t make eye

00:50:56.400 --> 00:50:58.040
contact with your partner.

00:50:59.560 --> 00:51:02.840
Basically, pick the person you feel the most with.

00:51:05.560 --> 00:51:08.240
Okay, let’s begin.

00:51:09.000 --> 00:51:11.000
Alright.

